1. *Oduvijek* sam želeo da posetim Novi Sad. (I have always wanted to visit Novi Sad.)
2. Njih dvoje su *oduvijek* bili najbolji prijatelji. (They have always been best friends.)
3. Ona je *oduvijek* bila talentovana za muziku. (She has always been talented in music.)
4. *Oduvijek* sam znao da ćeš uspeti. (I have always known that you will succeed.)
5. *Oduvijek* sam živeo u ovom gradu. (I have always lived in this city.)
6. Da li *oduvijek* piješ kafu bez šećera? (Have you always been drinking coffee without sugar?)
7. Njeni roditelji su *oduvijek* bili protiv te veze. (Her parents have always been against that relationship.)
8. *Oduvijek* se bavim sportom. (I have always been involved in sports.)
9. Oni su *oduvijek* živeli zajedno. (They have always lived together.)
10. *Oduvijek* sam se osećao kao da ne pripadam ovom svetu. (I have always felt like I don't belong in this world.)

Note: The word "oduvijek" is used as an adverb in all of the above sentences and it means "always" or "forever". The word is marked with an asterisk (*) in each sentence.